 <P>Of porenesse in spiri&yogh;t crist speke&thorn; &amp;
 sei&thorn; i-blessed ben pore men in spyri&yogh;t&middot; for &thorn;e kyng|dom of heuene is heres&middot; &amp; woo to riche men&middot;
