 &yogh;ow of litul fei&thorn;&middot; &para;And &thorn;erfore be &yogh;e not besy sey|ing what schul we ete&middot; or what schulle we dri|nk or how schullen we ben clo&thorn;ed&middot; for alle &thorn;es &thorn;in|ges mysbeleued men enqueren&middot; &amp; &thorn;erfore seche&thorn; first
