 pore in spiri&yogh;t&middot; &amp; leue&thorn; couetise / &yogh;if &yogh;e &thorn;inken co|me to heuene&middot; for coueytise is a seruice of fals
 goddis as seynt poule sei&thorn;&middot; &amp; siche schul not haue

