 <P>&para;Chastite is &thorn;e sixte
 vertu &thorn;at come&thorn; ou&yogh;t of loue&middot; &amp; norysche&thorn; loue&middot;
 &para;Also for he &thorn;at loue&thorn; god nyl not take no
