 seyde summe tyme &thorn;ou schalt doon no lecherie
 but I seye &yogh;ow who &thorn;at se&thorn; a womman&middot; for to couey|ten hire&middot; he ha&thorn; doon lecherye in his herte&middot; wi&thorn; &thorn;at
 womman &para; And &thorn;erfore &yogh;if &thorn;i ri&yogh;t eye sclaundre &thorn;e
 pul hym ou&yogh;t&middot; &amp; &thorn;row hym a wey from &thorn;e for
 hit is spedeful to &thorn;e &thorn;at on of &thorn;i membris per|ysche&middot; &thorn;an al &thorn;i body go in to &thorn;e fuyr of helle &amp;
 &yogh;if &thorn;i ri&yogh;t hond sclaundre &thorn;e kytte hym of &amp; &thorn;ro|we hym a wey fro &thorn;e&middot; for it is spedful to &thorn;e &thorn;at
 oon of &thorn;in membris perische &thorn;an al &thorn;i body go
 in to &thorn;e fuyr of helle&middot; Crist sei&thorn; also it was sey|de summe tyme&middot; who &thorn;at leue&thorn; his wif&middot; &yogh;eue he hi|re a libel of hire puttyng a wey&middot; but I seye &yogh;ow
 he &thorn;at leue&thorn; his wyf&middot; but it be for cause of for|nicacioun he make&thorn; hire do lecherie&middot; &amp; he &thorn;at wed|de&thorn; a womman &thorn;at is left of hire housbonde bre|ke&thorn; spousehed&middot;<NOTE>Mt 5.27-32</NOTE> &para; And in a tyme &thorn;e pharisees axe|den crist whe&thorn;er it where lefful to leuen to a man
 his wif for any enchesoun&middot; &amp; he seyde ne haue &yogh;e
 not rad &thorn;at he <DEL>&thorn;at<GAP></DEL> &thorn;at made man from &thorn;e be|gynnyng made &amp; womman &amp; seyde&middot; herfore aman
 schal leuen fadir &amp; modir and drawen hym to
 his wyf&middot; And &thorn;ei schul<DEL>de</DEL> be two in oon flesch&middot;
 But now &thorn;ei ben not two but oon fleysch&middot; &amp;
 &thorn;erefore &thorn;at god ha&thorn; ioyned no man departe&middot;

