 who &thorn;at weddi&thorn; a womman &thorn;at is lefte of hire
 housbonde&middot; do&thorn; <DEL>fornicacioun</DEL> lecherie<NOTE>Mt 19.3-9</NOTE></P>
 <P>&amp; &thorn;oo seyden
