 <P>Sire in &thorn;es two comaundementes of loue
 is al goodnesse fulfild&middot; &amp; al euel eschewed&middot; &amp;
 so &thorn;e lyuynge of oure soule &amp; &thorn;e ri&yogh;t weye to
